cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on object detection from videos using deep learning frameworks, specifically convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel framework that improves the state-of-the-art performance, which is related to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of deep learning frameworks also falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of contextual information, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
